'''比奇特尔公司'''（{{lang-en|'''Bechtel Corporation'''}}，又譯'''比奇特尔集团'''、'''贝克特尔公司'''）是美国最大的[[建筑|建筑]]和[[工程|工程]]公司<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://enr.construction.com/toplists/contractors/001-100.asp |title=ENR Top 400 |accessdate=2014-04-30 |archive-date=2013-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131226114543/http://enr.construction.com/toplists/contractors/001-100.asp |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在美国私营公司中排名第五<ref>Forbes 2011 - [http://www.forbes.com/lists/2011/21/private-companies-11_Bechtel_800U.html America's Largest Private Companies] {{Wayback|url=http://www.forbes.com/lists/2011/21/private-companies-11_Bechtel_800U.html |date=20170204052812 }}</ref>。总部在[[旧金山|旧金山]][[旧金山金融区|金融区]]<ref>{{cite news | author=David Streitfield; Mark Fineman | title=Bechtel Corporation Receives Iraqi Reconstruction Contract | url=http://tech.mit.edu/V123/N20/long_2_$20.20w.html | work=The Los Angeles Times | date= | accessdate= | archive-date=2016-03-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306090919/http://tech.mit.edu/V123/N20/long_2_$20.20w.html | dead-url=no }} posted in ''[[The_Tech_(newspaper)|The Tech]]''. '''vol. 123''', Issue 20. Friday, April 18, 2003. Retrieved 29 August 2010.</ref>。截至2012年，比奇特尔公司有379亿美元的收入和在近50个国家雇佣超過五萬三千名名员工<ref name=bechtelreport2011>{{cite web | author= | title=Annual Report | url=http://www.bechtel.com/2013-05-17.html | publisher=Bechtel | year=2012 | accessdate=9 October 2012 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130906031842/http://www.bechtel.com/2013-05-17.html | archivedate=2013年9月6日 }}</ref>。

